AFFIDAVIT OF NON-RECEIPT OF MAINTENANCE ASSESSMENTS
OF THE 281 EAST HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION AKA MOUNTAIN LODGE
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
"Notice is hereby given that there exists a lien for unpaid maintenance assessments assessed by 281 EAST HOMEOWNERS
ASSOCIATION AKA MOUNTAIN LODGE, for non-payment by the owner of the subject property and such maintenance assessments
being in accordance with the Master Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for 281 East Land as recorded in Volume
8202, Page 524 et seq. of the Official Public Records of Real Property Records of Bexar County, Texas; Amendment to Master
Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for 281 East Land as recorded in Volume 10774, Page 1422 et seq. of the
Official Public Records of Real Property Records of Bexar County, Texas; Supplemental Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and
Restrictions for Mountain Lodge as recorded in Volume 8205, Page 516 et seq. of the Official Public Records of Real Property
Records of Bexar County; Second Amendment to Master Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for 281 East Land,
Volume 11189 Page 1411 et seq. of the Official Public Records of Real Property Records of Bexar County; Texas; Third Amendment
to Master Declaration of Covenants, Conditions, and Restrictions for 281 East Land, refiled on September 19, 2006, as recorded in
Volume 12399 Page 1928 et seq. of Official Public Records of Real Property Records of Bexar County, Texas; Fourth Amendment to
Master Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for 281 East Land, as recorded in Volume 14213 Page 40 et seq. of the
Official Public Records of real property Records of Bexar County Texas; Fifth Amendment to Master Declaration of Covenants,
Conditions and Restrictions for 281 East Land, San Antonio, Texas as recorded in Volume 16967 Page 2130 et seq. of the Official
Public Records of Real Property Records of Bexar County, Texas. The property subject to this Affidavit is as follows, to-wit:
SUBJECT PROPERTY:
Address:
23434 Seven Winds, San Antonio, Texas 78258
Legal Description:
Lot 16, Block 7, Mountain Lodge, Unit 5B, (Planned Unit Development), Bexar County,
Texas, according to the map or plat thereof recorded in Volume 9570, Page 150, Real
Property Records, Bexar County, Texas.
Last Known Owners:
G&G Flomar, LLC
Last Known Address:
23434 Seven Winds, San Antonio, Texas 78258
Amount of Delinquent:
$1,350.54
Assessments and Fees:
Amounts are subject to continued accrual of late fees, interest and collection costs which
shall be automatically added to the lien amount.
Executed this day of _Jersey , 2022 .
281 EAST HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION AKA MOUNTAIN LODGE
By:
DIAMOND ASSOCIATION MANAGEMENT AND CONSULTING
By:
.:
RODNEY HERRERA
Its:
Association Manager
14603 Huebner Road, Building 40
San Antonio, Texas 78230
Phone: (210) 561-0606
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
This instrument is acknowledged and sworn to before me on this
4 day & January 2022 , by RODNEY
HERRERA, Association Manager of DIAMOND ASSOCIATION MANAGEMENT AND CONSULTING, on behalf of 281 EAST

SOTARY
PUBLIC
